item.title: CVE-2018-1248|2024-08-05T03:51:49.048Z -- dell%20emc -- rsa%20authentication%20manager%20security%20console%2C%20operation%20console%20and%20self-service%20console
item.description: RSA Authentication Manager Security Console, Operation Console and Self-Service Console, version 8.3 and earlier, is affected by a Host header injection vulnerability. This could allow a remote attacker to potentially poison HTTP cache and subsequently redirect users to arbitrary web domains.
